        }
    }
}
```
**Step 5: Test the profiler and injection**

* Build both projects and place the resulting DLLs in the same directory
* Run the injector program (Injector.exe)
* Verify that the profiler is initialized and shutdown correctly
* Check if the injected method (`DoSomething`) is called when expected

This is just a high-level outline of the steps involved. You may encounter issues or nuances specific to your environment, so be prepared to debug and adapt as needed.

